Package: teatimer
Title: Timer with an Alarm
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(c("Geoffrey", "Thompson"),email="gzthompson@gmail.com",
role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2436-8822")))	
Description: A rough timer which will play a notification sound after a specified number of minutes or seconds. It is intended to be useful if you want a reminder in 3 minutes that your tea is ready.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
